누적되면 사업 패턴이 보입니다</span>\n      </li>\n      <li style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:14px;color:var(--fg)\">\n        <span style=\"flex-shrink:0;width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--soft);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;margin-top:1px\">03</span>\n        <span>자동화 설정 1회. 이후엔 답만 적으면 됩니다</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-top:8px\">\n      <a href=\"#enroll\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;background:var(--brand);color:#FBF8F3;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:600;border-radius:var(--radius-card);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:.02em\">코스 시작하기</a>\n      <a href=\"#preview\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:14px;color:var(--brand);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;opacity:.75\">무료 미리보기 →</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <figure style=\"margin:0;border-radius:var(--radius-card);overflow:hidden;background:var(--soft);aspect-ratio:4/3;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center\">\n    <img src=\"/assets/placeholder/hero-editorial.svg\" alt=\"5분 하루 회고 루틴 시각화\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block\">\n  </figure>\n</div>",
