        "html": "<div class=\"wrap\" style=\"max-width:100%;padding:80px 5vw 72px;background:var(--bg);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;position:relative;overflow:hidden\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:42%;height:100%;background:var(--soft);clip-path:polygon(12% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);z-index:0\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:42%;height:100%;z-index:1;overflow:hidden\">\n    <img src=\"/assets/placeholder/hero-fullbleed-texture.svg\" alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;opacity:.18;mix-blend-mode:luminosity\">\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:680px\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--brand);margin:0 0 28px;font-weight:600\">Claude &times; 코어 캠퍼스</p>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif KR',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5.5vw,72px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.14;color:var(--accent);margin:0 0 24px\">\n      오늘 하루,<br>\n      <span style=\"color:var(--brand)\">5분이면</span><br>\n      충분합니다\n    </h1>\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:clamp(15px,1.5vw,19px);line-height:1.8;color:var(--fg);opacity:.78;max-width:520px;margin:0 0 36px\">\n      회고를 시작하지 못한 건 의지의 문제가 아닙니다.<br>\n      시스템이 없었을 뿐입니다. Claude가 대신 물어보고,<br>\n      당신은 짧게 답하기만 합니다.\n    </p>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;align-items:center\">\n      <a href=\"#enroll\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;background:var(--brand);color:var(--bg);font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;border-radius:var(--radius-card);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:.03em\">지금 시작하기</a>\n      <a href=\"#how\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:14px;color:var(--brand);text-decoration:none;opacity:.85;border-bottom:1px solid currentColor;padding-bottom:1px\">어떻게 작동하나요?</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative;z-index:2;margin-top:56px;display:flex;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif KR',Georgia,serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--brand)\">5분</span>\n      <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:12px;color:var(--fg);opacity:.6;letter-spacing:.04em\">하루 소요 시간</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width:1px;background:var(--soft)\"></div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif KR',Georgia,serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--brand)\">1회</span>\n      <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:12px;color:var(--fg);opacity:.6;letter-spacing:.04em\">자동화 초기 설정</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width:1px;background:var(--soft)\"></div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif KR',Georgia,serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--brand)\">30일</span>\n      <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:12px;color:var(--fg);opacity:.6;letter-spacing:.04em\">패턴이 보이는 시점</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
